{"tid":823473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人正面迎超強颱風山竹　各出奇招","createTime":"2018-09-16T23:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T00:08:55.000Z","uid":53524,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"855eb85de6d644e427d524eef6311d2e4ede0019","tid":823473,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:04:40.000Z","msg":"超強颳風山竹今天以狂風掃落葉姿態，強勢吹襲香港，中心風力時速達175公里！正當香港大部分市民嚴陣以待時，有人卻以獨特的方式迎接這個世紀強風。  （大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180916/640_d3c9e3d112f4471bc27d007b7f9316ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180916%2F640_d3c9e3d112f4471bc27d007b7f9316ce.jpg&h=cb36a052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港一巿民在尖沙嘴海邊感受山竹的威力。香港《蘋果》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180916/640_e768045defb49843bc7f35c3eeab5cbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180916%2F640_e768045defb49843bc7f35c3eeab5cbc.jpg&h=2e5dbd49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩位攝影愛好者，為了拍攝獨特角度，不顧自己和攝影器材盡濕。香港《蘋果》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180916/640_0ccfb12d7757ec455a9587fcb9c14891.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180916%2F640_0ccfb12d7757ec455a9587fcb9c14891.jpg&h=7608439b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這位市民內心激動。香港《蘋果》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180916/640_3e97848616eb267dc02e1bbcf414fc34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180916%2F640_3e97848616eb267dc02e1bbcf414fc34.jpg&h=ccc43cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n單腳迎接超強颱風。香港《蘋果》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180916/640_96513082e3a4f4d619303f6882b5ff6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180916%2F640_96513082e3a4f4d619303f6882b5ff6a.jpg&h=c85f093b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這位先生不畏颱風，在尖沙嘴表演薩克斯風。香港《蘋果》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180916/640_dd2ad8f6d65abf14fd020673df966f07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180916%2F640_dd2ad8f6d65abf14fd020673df966f07.jpg&h=789e1347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一班南亞裔人士在海旁湊熱鬧。香港《蘋果》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180916/640_8dfb76a89419802e16bc5d4ec8f0bc2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180916%2F640_8dfb76a89419802e16bc5d4ec8f0bc2f.jpg&h=5c7f0bd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在堅尼地城海旁一外籍人士突然興起，一頭就栽入已淹水的岸邊馬路「暢泳」。"},{"pid":"c5720ad2ffcc28c5a6920ab90ed014fda006277a","tid":823473,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:07:12.000Z","msg":"單腳都係企得穩<br />\n仲有人話個風勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3370783a12d4621180b0fc360b2b8da9f8d6f2e0","tid":823473,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:59:25.000Z","msg":"又話海邊浸禮取消咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d3f1369786bd6f95107ad6ef59fbc596b9bb41","tid":823473,"uid":133896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3370783a12d4621180b0fc360b2b8da9f8d6f2e0","tid":823473,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:59:25.000Z","msg":"又話海邊浸禮取消咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:05:01.000Z","msg":"其他人照常浸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cf2d6253b61385109b1f1015b3fa85b4479215","tid":823473,"uid":87064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:05:57.000Z","msg":"誠心崇拜"},{"pid":"38f0ae4f82fd192231c2fd568138b9dab1afc794","tid":823473,"uid":123969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:08:55.000Z","msg":"吹撚曬啲南亞人返鄉下就啱"}]}